data.title: About: Deepfield
data.meta_description: Deepfield (often stylized as deepfield) are an American rock band from Charleston, South Carolina, consisting of members Baxter Teal III, Jake Portenkirchner, Ken Becker and PJ Farley. They have released three albums and one EP. The band is currently based in Chicago, Illinois.
data.text:
dbo:abstract

Deepfield (oft auch: deepfield) ist eine US-amerikanische Alternative-Rock-Band aus Charleston, South Carolina, mit Baxter Teal III, Aron Robinson, Ken Becker und PJ Farley als Bandmitglieder. In den USA haben sie bisher zwei Alben und eine EP veröffentlicht. Ihr Musikstil wird als Alternative Rock und Post-Grunge eingestuft. Die Band ist derzeit in Chicago, Illinois zu Hause. (de)

Deepfield (often stylized as deepfield) are an American rock band from Charleston, South Carolina, consisting of members Baxter Teal III, Jake Portenkirchner, Ken Becker and PJ Farley. They have released three albums and one EP. The band is currently based in Chicago, Illinois. (en)

I Deepfield sono una band alternative rock e post-grunge statunitense composta da Baxter Teal III, Aron Robinson, Sean Von Tersch e PJ Farley. Hanno pubblicato due album e un EP. (it)
